<svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 32 32" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> <!-- Background circle --> <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="14" fill="url(#faviconGradient)" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="1.5"/>
<!-- Bodyweight exercise icon (pull-up bar with figure) --> <g transform="translate(16, 16)"> <!-- Pull-up bar --> <rect x="-8" y="-6" width="16" height="1.5" fill="white" rx="0.75"/> <!-- Bar supports --> <rect x="-9" y="-6" width="1" height="4" fill="white" rx="0.5"/> <rect x="8" y="-6" width="1" height="4" fill="white" rx="0.5"/>
<!-- Figure doing pull-up --> <!-- Head --> <circle cx="0" cy="-3" r="1.5" fill="white"/> <!-- Body --> <rect x="-0.75" y="-1.5" width="1.5" height="4" fill="white" rx="0.75"/> <!-- Arms reaching up to bar --> <path d="M -0.75 -1 L -4 -5" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/> <path d="M 0.75 -1 L 4 -5" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/> <!-- Legs (slightly bent) --> <path d="M -0.5 2.5 L -1.5 6" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/> <path d="M 0.5 2.5 L 1.5 6" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/> </g>
<!-- Gradient definition --> <defs> <linearGradient id="faviconGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%"> <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#8b5cf6;stop-opacity:1" /> <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#6366f1;stop-opacity:1" /> </linearGradient> </defs> </svg>
